snippet.title: MUST SEE Erika Kirk and Barron Trump Sing Tribute to Charlie Kirk "We Lift Our Eyes To God" AI Cover
snippet.description:
MUST-WATCH MOMENT: In a stunning and deeply emotional performance, Barron Trump and Erika Kirk come together for a one-of-a-kind musical tribute to honor the life and legacy of Charlie Kirk.

Erika Kirk, Charlie’s widow, joins Barron to sing their original song, "Our God Is Good," an anthem of faith, strength, and unwavering hope in the face of tragedy and loss. This performance is an absolute must-see, offering a powerful message of comfort and resilience that has captivated the world.

The song's core message—that faith provides an anchor in the storm—is breathtaking. Listen for this incredibly powerful Chorus:

We lift our eyes to God above,
The One who saves, the God of love.
Every step, we walk by faith,
Guided by His endless grace.
From the mountains high to the valleys low,
We’ll sing His name so all may know:
Our God is good, forever true,
And all we are, we give to You.

If this song touches your heart, please Like, Share, and Subscribe for more inspiring content. Leave a comment below with which lyric resonated with you the most.
